# OpenSecKit Security Instructions

This project uses **OpenSecKit v{{ version }}** for security-as-code workflows with a hub-and-spokes architecture.

## Project Structure (V4)

```
.osk/
├── system-model/      # Hub: System documentation (always read first)
│   ├── index.yaml     # Quick stats and cross-references (~200 lines)
│   ├── business.yaml  # Business context and processes
│   ├── architecture.yaml
│   ├── data.yaml      # Data inventory with classifications
│   ├── actors.yaml
│   ├── trust.yaml     # Trust zones and boundaries
│   ├── integrations.yaml
│   ├── security.yaml
│   └── gaps.yaml
├── compliance/        # Spoke: Compliance assessments
│   └── assessment-*.yaml
└── specs/             # Spoke: Feature security specifications
    └── NNN-feature/
```

